        }
      },
      "methods": [],
      "module_path": "dry_check",
      "docs": "Coverage manifest written by `dry write` and consumed by `dry check-approved` for staleness checking (D5). Records the set of FragmentRef values (path + content_hash) for all diff fragments processed in the most recent `dry write` run. If a current diff fragment's FragmentRef is absent from this set, `check-approved` returns Blocked (stale coverage), so the same content hash at a different path is not treated as covered. BTreeSet preserves deterministic serialization order (CN-05).",
